name: Intradebook
overview:
A B2B site and interactive software to internationalize Small Enterprises and untangle routine of export and import, with all alternatives trading, freight and payment.

The InTrade software directs and performs, step-by-step, all export and import operations. 1008 alternatives of trade, each with 70 steps on average, which generates more than 70,000 questions “yes” or “no”, fully interactive and accessible language, original, to make the connection between theory and practice of international trade for Small Businesses, compiling more than 2,000 hours of surfing with all the steps and documents of foreign trade.

1 - Software InTrade, with free licenses. 2 - Site InTradeBook.com, to support market information, operational information, supply and demand for products, service and supply and demand for jobs in the field of foreign trade.
